    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p>",
